COMMUNITY / CONTENT SAFETY GUIDELINES

Kiddotubes is for children — content must be age-appropriate, non-violent, non-sexual, and free from hate speech.

No bullying or targeted harassment.

No personal contact info of children (full name, address, school) in public uploads or comments.

Moderation: uploads may be reviewed by humans and automated filters. Parents can flag content. Violations result in remove/warning/suspension.

Reporting: provide a “Report” button on video pages and a parental contact form.